<br>
SCM 3 adds 10% total upgrade (saves 10% mana on every cast) and SCF 3 adds 7% overall damage (provided none are wasted on kill shots etc.) and add SCFM 3 and it adds another 6% total damage upgrade. So even with all 3 of these added together instead of just the two you listed, your output has increased only 23%. Not 35-40%.<br>
<br>
Just wanted to clear that up.<br>
<br>
Also wanted to point out that if you fight mobs with high HP (umbral plains, kael, CT) our total dps numbers will suffer compared to melee because the longer the fight, effectively the more uptime you have, the worse the wizzy does.<br>
<br>
The original poster made his post reagrding his actual logs and his actual gear in a specific circumstance. He is not saying he &quot;feels&quot; like this or that so we should respect at least his conclusions about that particular situation. if it does not fit into our other data then perhaps our other data does not take that specific circumstance into account.<br>
<br>
just some thoughts,<br>
